content:
New Objects in Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator

Do more with these new Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator objects.

Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new FulfillmentAsset object.
Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new FulfillmentAssetAttribute object.
Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new FulfillmentFalloutRule object.
Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new FulfillmentStepJeopardyRule object.
Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new ProductFulfillmentDecompRule object.
Define a step that must be executed during fulfillment orchestration
Use the new FulfillmentStepDefinition object.

Create a group of fulfillment step definitions
Use the new FulfillmentStepDefinitionGroup object.
Create a dependency between two fulfillment step definitions
Use the new FulfillmentStepDependencyDefinition object.
Create a link between a product and the corresponding group of fulfillment steps that's necessary to fulfill that product
Use the new ProductFulfillmentScenario object.
Associate a fulfillment step with a type, such as a callout or manual task
Use the new FulfillmentStepType object.

Create a graphic view of the setup steps required to fulfill an order
Use the new FulfillmentPlan object.
Create a fulfillment step that executes during fulfillment of an order
Use the new FulfillmentStep object.
Create a dependency between two fulfillment steps
Use the new FulfillmentStepDependency object.
Create a link between a fulfillment step and corresponding order lines
Use the new FulfillmentStepSource object.

Create mappings between fields and attributes within decomposition
Use the new ValTfrm object.
Create a rule that determines how an order is broken into sub-orders with specific technical details that help in order fulfillment
Use the new ValTfrmGrp object.
Define mappings between fields and attributes for decomposition
Use the new ProductDecompEnrichmentRule object.

Create information about the attributes that are used in the definition for a fulfillment step group
Use the new FulfillmentWorkspaceItem object.
Create a visual designer for fulfillment plans
Use the new FulfillmentWorkspace object.
Define a set of steps to be created to fulfill the order
Use the new FulfillmentPlan object.

Define a relationship between a fulfillment order line and its decomposition source
Use the new FulfillmentLineSourceRel object.
Define a relationship between two fulfillment order lines
Use the new FulfillmentLineRel object.
Create an attribute of a fulfillment order line
Use the new FulfillmentLineAttribute object.
Create a relationship between two fulfillment assets
Use the new FulfillmentAssetRelationship object.
title: New Features in Salesforce Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator
